IN RE ESTATE OF HOLMES 2019-0743 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 11, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due June 6, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed. Appellant's motion for immediate stay denied as moot.
